<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06054g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06054g">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06054g"> 54(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> bit of t<font color="green">[issue]</font> necklaces / fichu</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Cette petite cr&eacute;ature qui n&apos;a en partage que ses yeux bleus, sa placidit&eacute;, ses joues roses et un sourire &eacute;ternel sur ses l&egrave;vres de cerise, quelle imagination il faut pour l&apos;habiller d&apos;un <mark>chiffon d&apos;indienne</mark> qui sera la robe, d&apos;une rognure de tulle qui sera le <mark>fichu</mark> &hellip;! <font color="green">[This little creature who shares only her blue eyes, her placidity, her pink cheeks and an eternal smile on her cherry lips, what imagination it takes to dress her with an Indian rag that will be the dress, a bunch of tulle that will be the damn ...!]</font> <small> Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Queyrat, <a name="FQLJ" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FQLJ"><cite title="source">Les Jeux des Enfants</cite></a> (1920) 125</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c01125d" href="c01all.htm#c01125d">VI.C.01:125(d)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
